title: The Sheriff and the Satellite Kid [1979]
description:
Sheriff and the Satellite Kid

Starring Bud Spencer, Cary Guffey, Raimund Harmstorf, Joe Bugner

Running time 95 minutes

The Sheriff and the Satellite Kid (Italian: Uno sceriffo extraterrestre - poco extra e molto terrestre) is a 1979 Italian children's comedy film starring Bud Spencer and child actor Cary Guffey that was released in cinemas in 197.
